{"tid":2424978,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韋利安承認被迫落「車」入「廠」","createTime":"2021-02-27T04:44:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T11:33:24.000Z","uid":31314,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0b250fafd3d6c9df2b7f9e4d3f27c21b0e4c793f","tid":2424978,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:44:14.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴翼鋒韋利安承認，從來都不想出走車路士，只是對方未能滿足合約要求，被逼離隊。韋利安（Willian）約滿今季離開效力了7年的車路士，以自由身加盟同市宿敵阿仙奴，「作出這個決定真的很難，因為兩家球會之間的競爭非常激烈。我需要經過深思熟慮，和妻子及經理人都討論了很多次。」<br />\n<br />\n這名32歲巴西國腳直言，本想一直為車路士披甲，「我離開不是因為不和，大家都知道我真的很想留下來，只是最終沒有達成協議。我要求3年合約，車路士只想給2年，這就是我最終離開的原因。」<br />\n<br />\n韋利安表示選擇兵工廠，<strong><span class=\"red\">全因被領隊阿迪達、總監伊度說服，「他們想改變球會的理念，讓阿仙奴可以再次於英超爭霸，再次征戰歐聯。</span></strong>」不過，兵工廠未能反彈，今輪前僅排第11位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿林納<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c0f16853c028c3b8aca7be2180ce89010a7ac4d","tid":2424978,"uid":7585,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:48:30.000Z","msg":"金章安喺阿森納留唔留到2季<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7e912152c337f8c1ed0d1c8a0762b537b9fa7fd","tid":2424978,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:51:18.000Z","msg":"安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e4121ff0b1a792630f683bdd6aa142bdc7b7a2","tid":2424978,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"為理念之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178589f859157e3004228490ec2987bfa7e50fa","tid":2424978,"uid":54025,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"